Below the link cards: a 1px divider (`border-tertiary`) full-width, then the META meta-row with these fields (in this order, gap `space/600`):

| Label | Value | Font |
|---|---|---|
| `GENERATED` | ISO timestamp the agent stamped when this card was last rebuilt, e.g. `2026-05-12 15:43 UTC` | Geist Mono Regular 13, `text-primary` |
